com.daohoangson.uml.parser
Class Parser

java.lang.Object
  com.daohoangson.uml.parser.Parser

public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object

A Jave source parser. It makes use of LexicalAnalyzer and put structure found into a diagram. Parse everything from Class/Interface to Argument. The content of methods is ignored.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Dao Hoang Son
